    "plan_content": "## Plan Summary\n\n**Root cause:** Classic off-by-one error in `src/utils.ts` at line 7.\n\n```typescript\n// BUGGY — the `- 1` causes the loop to stop before the last element\nfor (let i = 0; i < items.length - 1; i++) {\n\n// FIXED\nfor (let i = 0; i < items.length; i++) {\n```\n\n**Impact:** Three of the four existing `processItems` tests in `tests/utils.test.ts` were already written to catch this exact behavior — they'll all pass after the single-character fix.\n\n**Scope:** One line changed in one file (`src/utils.ts`). No other files need modification.",
